data.description: Exquisite! This home is absolutely stunning and ready for you to move right in. Don't wait for new construction, pack your boxes and Welcome Home! Situated in the highly desired Choral Series at River Island Ranch in Visalia. Located near Riverway Sports Park, Valley Oaks Golf Course and tons of shopping and dining. As you drive up to this beautiful property you will notice the modern design and immaculate yard. This Next Gen home provides the opportunity for a private living space for a multi generational family with a living room, bathroom, laundry closet and bedroom with a private entrance. When you enter the home you are greeted with beautiful wood laminate flooring that leads you to the grand stair case and open concept living space. Entertaining is a dream, never miss a thing while cooking and be a part of all the action. The kitchen is the heart of the home with a oversized center kitchen island with a generous size breakfast bar. The quartz countertops perfectly compliment the subway tile backsplash, dark wood cabinets and designer lighting. The Stainless steel appliances include built in fridge, gas stove/oven, microwave and dishwasher. To compliment the open entertaining space this home has to offer is a formal dining space with large windows to let in the natural lighting. Step up wide stair case to your second story living. A large open space loft is available  that offers endless potential for an office, game room or even a workout studio! Don't drag your laundry up and down the stairs, this home has 2nd story laundry and storage closet close to all the bedrooms for easy folding and put away. There are two additional spare bedrooms and a guest bathroom with dual sinks. The primary bedroom a large walk in closet, oversized shower, dual sinks and natural lighting. Custom paint and window coverings throughout. This home is truly a must see!
